history.content:
I would not expect it to be the same next year -- from looking at past exams, it's usually much more programming based. I'm in it this semester (it's awesome so far), and there hasn't been a lot of programming. It's being taught by a visiting lecturer, so I'd base any expectations for the course next semester on previous semesters with Berkeley faculty.
